{"tid":1509600,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黑警還眼? 我還你老母","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:26:13.000Z","uid":3456,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a70fc1defc7e2b52d3af216ba4dc6ad2c6652388","tid":1509600,"uid":3456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:52:05.000Z","msg":"其實一直唔明大家點解見到班狗要大叫呢句<br />\n我明白呢句係對外國文宣有用<br />\n但你想班狗聽到呢句之後會點?<br />\n會打爆隻眼比番你?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人地笑鳩我地 當呢個係戰績黎咋</span><br />\n你地用人地戰績黎幫做口號 係咪傻嫁<br />\n有d和理仲要遮住自己對眼<br />\n我係狗我真係笑鳩你地<br />\n正如我地一諗起無名指就會陰陰咀笑話人抵死一樣<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎都有人叫 對班狗 一定要叫支持警察 吞槍自殺<br />\n目的唔係要佢真係自殺呀<br />\n係要佢連支持佢既人都唔信呀<br />\n當你被日日洗腦 支持警察吞槍自殺<br />\n當你有日係街邊聽到支持警察 你個腦就自然諗佢會唔會有下句<br />\n所以大家唔好再叫黑警還眼啦好嘛<br />\n跟我一齊大叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持警察 吞槍自殺!</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cb483ec0f0c466d5a77677c7bac781726433fcd","tid":1509600,"uid":3456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"支持警察 吞槍自殺!"},{"pid":"da25abc3c44a3b2e3b804c047ef2dad35d5d3551","tid":1509600,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=084cb2d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=614ce77e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data